com.amazon.carbonado.raw

Class DataDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazon.carbonado.raw.DataDecoder

  • public class DataDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
    A very low-level class that decodes key components encoded by methods of DataEncoder.
    Author:
    Brian S O'Neill
    See Also:
    KeyDecoder
